## How to Run the Project

### Prerequisites

* Java JDK 8+
* Maven
* Google Chrome

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/thuantcn1802/Automation-Test-Guru99-Bank.git
cd Automation-Test-Guru99-Bank
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
mvn clean install
```

### Execute Tests

```bash
mvn test
```

